      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver convergence to be documented; not required beyond Gradation 1 at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 the required level for numerical solver error is Gradation 1 (awareness). Residual convergence to 1e-5 is logged for all simulations; no further formal assessment is required under the MRL 2 plan."
    },
